UserImg" loading="lazy"><br>Also, All The President's Men also made <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deep_Throat_(Watergate)" rel="nofollow noopener">Deep Throat</a> a household term.</span></div><div class=""></div></div></section></section><section class="ReviewCard__tags"><ul class="CollapsableList"><span tabindex="-1"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/8316749?shelf=hidden-quest" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">hidden-quest</span></a><span tabindex="-1"> </span><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/8316749?shelf=historical" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">historical</span></a><span tabindex="-1"> </span><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/8316749?shelf=non-fic-that-makes-learning-fun" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">non-fic-that-makes-learning-fun</span></a></span><span tabindex="-1"></span></ul></section><footer class="SocialFooter"><div data-testid="stats" class="SocialFooter__statsContainer"><div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--inline Button--small Button--subdued"><span class="Button__labelItem">17 likes</span></button></div></div><div data-testid="actions"><div class="SocialFooter__action"><div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--inline Button--small" aria-label="Review unliked. Press to like review"><span class="Button__labelItem"><i class="Icon LikeIcon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.4813282,6.41129383 L14.586127,6.97676447 C14.5964421,7.03541935 14.6071117,7.09675198 14.6181364,7.1607667 L14.8551301,8.60363442 L17.440983,8.60363442 C18.1623576,8.60363442 18.8218187,9.01120377 19.1444272,9.65642083 L19.1708204,9.70920723 C19.4523479,10.2722622 19.4523479,10.9350066 19.1708204,11.4980616 L19.118034,11.6036344 L19.1708204,11.7092072 C19.4523479,12.2722622 19.4523479,12.9350066 19.1708204,13.4980616 L1