, and I made a beeline to Amazon to order the book afterwards.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eBob Woodward and Carl Bernstein. Thank God that they pursued the story, always refusing to give up. Not only did Nixon get outed, this story taught people that if something nefarious and wicked is going on I our government, they can speak up rather than sitting in silence and fear.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eI think we probably owe a lot of current leaks during this Trump administration to the fact that Woodward and Bernstein taught the citizens of the United States that they can fight for truth, honesty, and justice.","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/5437232?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1950427481"},"likeCount":19,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":0},"User:8316749":{"id":8316749,"__typename":"User","legacyId":8316749,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1403245461i/8316749._UY200_CR64,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":818,"viewerRelationshipStatus":null,"name":"KatieMc","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/8316749-katiemc","contributor":null,"followersCount":87},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.jUSQHH_Kems9FAz-oBuubg":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.jUSQHH_Kems9FAz-oBuubg","__typename":"Review","creator":{"__ref":"User:8316749"},"recommendFor":null,"updatedAt":1614977808698,"createdAt":1406356028000,"spoilerStatus":false,"lastRevisionAt":1406357743000,"text":"This was probably the first non-fiction grown-up book I ever read. It's a compelling portrayal of an momentous slice of American history and journalism. This evening I went to an American Cinematheque screening of 1976 film adaptation of All The President's Men. Holy hotness, the camera sure does love Robert Redford.\u003cbr\u003e\u